name: Story Board of "Sisir Tanah - Bebal" (FJ Kunting Performance Art)
description:
This is the blue print or story board of the music video Sisir Tanah - Bebal. I made this story board in 2017 before producing the music video. If you watch the video maybe you can find a little difference or miss the concept, but I think this is normal in a artwork plan.

In 2017, I became the music video director for Sisir Tanah - Bebal. You can watch the music video on Youtube.
https://youtu.be/uN1O2bZdv0s

Actually, my first idea was to create a new story or a new meaning from FJ Kunting's performances, so I looked for possible media, such as performing arts, film, etc. Finally I chose a music video, because I think music is popular culture and this is a challenge for me to present performance art in pop culture, especially in Indonesia.
